data.description: Welcome to this wonderful Southwest style home! Step inside, the living area boasts high ceilings with exposed vigas, tongue groove and a wood burning fireplace. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor, offers a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms with access to the balconies. All while being centrally located minutes to dining and shopping.
